{
  "id": "RAW_e82038",
  "title": "【第 3493 期】{transitions} = f(state)",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3Es8QT1-tsqO-II03nafGw",
  "date": "2025-04-18 00:00:00",
  "author": "Jordan Eldredge",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">讨论了将 React 应用程序视为状态机器的好处，以及如何通过&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">{transitions} = f(state)</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;模型来防止用户触发无效的状态更新。今日前端早读课文章由 @Jordan Eldredge 分享，@飘飘翻译。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">译文从这开始～～</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px 1em;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(221, 221, 221);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“当前状态（state）决定了用户在这个状态下能进行哪些有效的操作（transitions）。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">通俗地说，你应用当前的状态不仅决定了界面要长什么样（这是 React 一直强调的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI = f(state)</span></code><span leaf=\"\">），它同时也决定了用户能点击哪些按钮、触发哪些事件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">简而言之：将 React 的组件树看作是一个状态机，有助于更清晰地理解异步更新和 React 并发特性的影响。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">状态机是一种描述具有状态且随时间变化的系统的形式化方法。它通常包括对系统可能处于的状态的明确定义，以及一个状态转换表，该表列举了在每个状态下可以进行哪些有效的状态转换（也就是哪些更新会让系统进入一个新的状态）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651251878&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a26de64a160f8339b4fca95e789a5f41&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第2497期】降低前端业务复杂度新视角：状态机范式\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第2497期】降低前端业务复杂度新视角：状态机范式</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以将一个 React 应用程序视为对状态机的建模。每一次渲染，都是从一个状态出发，生成对应的 UI。这也就是 React 著名的思维模型：</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI = f(state)</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。但在复杂应用中，想要正式列出一个状态转换表通常不可行。因为可能的状态数量是无限的，这种情况下我们就无法用表格描述所有转换，而是需要定义一个 “映射函数”：一个概念上的函数，它接收一个状态，并返回该状态下所有有效的状态转换。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你仔细观察，其实每个 React 应用已经隐式地定义了这样一个函数。开发者通过在组件中绑定事件处理函数（event handlers）到 DOM 上，来定义在某个状态下用户可以进行哪些有效的操作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，React 的组件树不仅是 “UI 是状态的函数”，它同时也定义了当前状态下哪些操作（状态转换）是有效的。同样可以简洁地表示为：</span></p>\n  <pre tabindex=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:10px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:3px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;overflow:auto;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;widows:2;font:400 13.6px / 1.45 Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;text-align:start;\"><code style=\"border:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:12px;line-height:inherit;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:normal;border-radius:5px;overflow:auto;word-break:normal;font-family:Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">{</span></span><span leaf=\"\">transitions</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">f</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span leaf=\"\">state</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">举个例子</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个 Todo 应用可能支持一个状态更新操作&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">complete(todoId)</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，它用来将某个待办事项标记为完成。如果用户试图 “完成” 一个已经被删除的 todo，那就会出错。最理想的情况是向用户显示一个错误弹窗，而最糟糕的情况则会导致出现 “TypeError： 无法设置未定义属性” 的 JavaScript 错误。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">用状态机的说法就是：对于一个不包含 id 为 x 的 todo 的状态来说，</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">complete(x)</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是一个无效的状态转换。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 的编程模型让我们能够很自然地避免这类错误。甚至可以说自然到我们根本没意识到这是个 “防错” 机制。如果某个 todo 被删除了，我们从状态中把它移除，那么对应的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;Todo /&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;组件就不会再被渲染，“完成” 按钮也就不再出现在界面上，用户自然也就无法点击，从而避免了无效的状态更新。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">请注意： 以上的机制依赖于 JavaScript 是单线程并且 UI 是阻塞式的。当我们同步更新应用程序的状态时，我们可以确信在浏览器响应更多用户输入之前，会先将这些状态更改刷新到用户界面。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">异步更新</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">一旦更新变成了异步的，我们就无法再 “自动” 获得这种防错机制了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如说，如果删除一个 todo 需要向后端发送网络请求，并且我们等请求完成之后才更新本地状态，那在这段等待期间，页面上可能仍然会渲染出这个被 “删除” 的 todo 的 “完成” 按钮，用户还是可以点击 —— 虽然这个操作在逻辑上已经是无效的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">这时候就需要我们手动防止用户触发这种无效操作。我们有两个常用的解决方案：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、乐观更新（optimistic update）</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">在网络请求还在进行时，先从本地状态中删除该 todo，这样它就不会再被渲染，也就避免了用户误操作的机会。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、设置 “处理中” 状态</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">保留这个 todo，但在状态中标记为 “处理中” 状态（pending），并禁用它的 “完成” 按钮，在请求完成之前不允许点击。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我们能同步更新这种 “乐观” 或 “pending” 的状态，那么&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">{transitions} = f(state)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这个模型就能继续帮我们阻止用户触发无效操作。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">并发更新</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 的某些并发特性（比如&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">startTransition</span></code><span leaf=\"\">）允许我们进行一种 “低优先级” 的状态更新，这种更新在浏览器向用户交出控制权之前不会立即刷新到 DOM。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就类似于异步更新，在一小段时间内，UI 可能会让用户触发一些我们其实不希望他们执行的操作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着，如果某次状态更新会影响用户能执行哪些操作（即状态转换），那我们就需要配合一个 “同步的乐观更新” 或 “pending 标记”，确保 UI 能立刻反映出某些按钮或操作被禁用了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">正因如此，<a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651275943&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e05bb050e11f14705c2eb6550b778a10&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"React\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">React</a>&nbsp;的很多并发特性都内置了这类机制支持，比如：</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">useTransition</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">useActionState</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">useFormStatus</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;提供了&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">isPending</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;标志位和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">useOptimistic</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;则允许我们配合一个低优先级的状态更新执行乐观更新</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">{transitions} = f(state)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是一个非常有用的思维模型，帮助我们思考如何防止用户触发无效的状态更新。它能帮助我们判断哪些更新可以异步或并发处理，哪些则必须同步处理来防止出错。它还让我们清楚地知道 React 组件在这个过程中的作用 —— 比如在哪些状态下需要渲染不同的 UI 来引导或限制用户操作。</span></p>\n  <section class=\"mp_common_product_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-product data-windowproduct=\"v2=HOqgHrWOnaUt1QvRo6NNdj49SD-qw6fcVBLYSXJMOnfCX6f8XiVaX7xYT745V2Pyjy1YRs2SAq7TdQ\" data-customstyle=\"{&quot;display&quot;:&quot;block&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:&quot;169px&quot;}\" data-cardtype=\"1\" data-title=\"低代码平台开发实践：基于React\" data-type=\"1\"></mp-common-product>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px !important;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关于本文</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">译者：@飘飘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：@Jordan Eldredge</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">https://jordaneldredge.com/blog/transitions-f-of-state/</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "本文提出将 React 组件视为状态机，通过 {transitions} = f(state) 模型来有效防止用户触发无效的状态更新，同时讨论了异步和并发更新场景下的处理方法。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文提出将 React 组件视为状态机，通过 {transitions} = f(state) 模型来有效防止用户触发无效的状态更新，同时讨论了异步和并发更新场景下的处理方法。",
  "summary": "文章探讨了将 React 应用程序视为状态机模型的益处，核心在于理解“当前状态决定了用户在该状态下能进行哪些有效的操作”。通过 {transitions} = f(state) 这一模型，开发者可以更清晰地处理异步和并发更新，防止用户触发无效状态更新。文章通过 Todo 应用的例子，说明了在同步更新时 React 的防错机制，并进一步讨论了在异步更新和并发更新场景下，如何利用乐观更新和“处理中”状态等方法，配合 React 内置的并发特性（如 useTransition、useActionState 和 useOptimistic），确保 UI 能及时反映状态变化，避免用户误操作。总结指出，该模型有助于判断哪些更新需要同步处理以防止出错，以及 React 组件如何引导或限制用户操作。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "{transitions} = f(state) 模型有助于防止无效状态更新",
      "explanation": "该模型强调状态决定了用户可执行的操作，通过在状态改变时同步更新 UI，避免用户在不正确的状态下触发操作。"
    },
    {
      "point": "异步更新可能导致用户触发无效操作",
      "explanation": "在异步更新期间，UI 可能未及时反映状态变化，允许用户执行逻辑上已失效的操作，需要手动防止。"
    },
    {
      "point": "并发更新需要配合同步的乐观更新或 pending 标记",
      "explanation": "React 的并发特性可能导致 UI 延迟更新，因此需要立即更新 UI 以禁用某些操作，防止用户触发无效状态转换。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "当前状态（state）决定了用户在这个状态下能进行哪些有效的操作（transitions）。",
    "可以将一个 React 应用程序视为对状态机的建模。每一次渲染，都是从一个状态出发，生成对应的 UI。",
    "{transitions} = f(state) 是一个非常有用的思维模型，帮助我们思考如何防止用户触发无效的状态更新。"
  ],
